{"metadata":{"title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L775","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordinate:animated:","platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"deprecated":true,"beta":false}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Deprecated. Sets the geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the user location is being tracked, with an optional transition animation."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"targetCoordinate"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view. If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":", the map fits the target instantaneously."}]}],"name":"animated"}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This method has no effect if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"userTrackingMode","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property is set to a value","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"other than ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To specify a completion handler to execute after the animation finishes, use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapVie